User can input a word to search out rhymes for.  The results are displayed in a list view on the same screen.  User can view the About page through the drop down menu action, 'About'.  On the about page, the user is also able to open a browser to the page of the RhymeBrain web service.  Sharing has been enabled for the currently viewed rhyme on the create/edit page.  When user changes the orientation in the Create/Edit activity, the layout will change accordingly for a more optimum user experience.\
\
